{"tid":2395855,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"毛孟靜指謀訂「假新聞法」針對記者","createTime":"2021-02-05T07:11:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-05T08:56:39.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"220237b8d3cdc1ee293c1dce7796cae98182d1dd","tid":2395855,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T07:11:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210205/NPJD7MHIBBCRVPBWMJH5VN55YA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210205%2FNPJD7MHIBBCRVPBWMJH5VN55YA%2F&d=GtJgxCFvwMhqeg%2B2Fxb9EY2ydpG6lAcy7lEd76f4zig%3D&h=a8951ef3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210205%2FNPJD7MHIBBCRVPBWMJH5VN55YA%2F&h=ed28c4ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210205/NPJD7MHIBBCRVPBWMJH5VN55YA/</a><br />\n<br />\n毛孟靜指謀訂「假新聞法」針對記者<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】特首林鄭月娥昨日除了提出將起底刑事化，又表明打擊發佈「虛假信息」、擾亂社會秩序等行為，曾任記者的前立法會議員毛孟靜形容，林鄭密謀訂立「假新聞法」，香港即時「大陸化」，變相成內地尋釁滋事罪，最後則引入記者記分制或發牌制度，新聞自由臨末日，市民日後難以發聲。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：趁火打劫  林鄭狂推爭議法案 起底擬刑事化<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥在立法會答問會主動提出將立法打。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/cWeefWCPs6DYC2WGs_5fOy85tRI=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2YB76POYUFFARDAB5D73XFOTQU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FcWeefWCPs6DYC2WGs_5fOy85tRI%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2YB76POYUFFARDAB5D73XFOTQU.jpg&h=76d66783&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n毛孟靜<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n憂如同內地尋釁滋事罪<br />\n<br />\n毛孟靜指，林鄭聲稱會參考外地立法和行政措施，但香港條件與西方社會不同，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n毛擔心當局持雙重標準，引入記者記分制或發牌制度，「會唔會親中報紙就。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭昨未有透露措施細節，本報。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"5b8ee4af04d4fedd69831288122493d41988e186","tid":2395855,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T07:25